[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      157[0m:[38;5;10m[49m | **Cost Estimate** | Neptune: ~$0.35/hr for db.r5.large (smallest production instance); add a read replica for CDS query isolation (~$504/month total for primary + replica). DynamoDB: on-demand pricing ~$1.25 per million writes. Lambda: negligible at typical query volumes. Monthly estimate for 500-bed hospital: $400-800/month (Neptune primary + read replica accounts for ~70% of cost). Scale linearly with pathway query volume. Add ~$200/month per additional read replica for high-query-volume deployments. |
