[0m[49m[39m  556, 575[0m:[39m[49m - **Recipe 13.4 (Drug-Drug Interaction Knowledge Base):** The allergy and drug interaction checks referenced in pathway conditions can leverage this recipe's interaction graph
[0m[49m[39m  557, 576[0m:[39m[49m - **Recipe 13.6 (Care Gap Reasoning Engine):** Uses similar ontological reasoning patterns but focused on preventive care guidelines rather than acute treatment pathways
